== Lius pi monumints ==

*  Capèle '''''Note-Danme d’chés Cinses''''' 
* Lius-dits deul Cinse du '''''P’tit Selve pi du Grand Selve''''', (i réste dés véstiges d’eune anthieusse conmind’rie d’chés timpliés ).
* carte postale ed l’école du Grand Boégny ;  pour vir l’carte postale =  [http://www.inrp.fr/mnemo/web/affiche_photo.php?url=a%3A7%3A%7Bs%3A6%3A%22interf%22%3Bs%3A2%3A%22fr%22%3Bs%3A10%3A%22nbe_photos%22%3Bs%3A1%3A%221%22%3Bs%3A12%3A%22offset_photo%22%3Bi%3A0%3Bs%3A14%3A%22liste_photo_id%22%3Bs%3A6%3A%2211451%2C%22%3Bs%3A5%3A%22titre%22%3Bs%3A29%3A%22Ecole+de+Buigny-les-Gamaches.%22%3Bs%3A5%3A%22type_%22%3Bs%3A13%3A%22Carte+postale%22%3Bs%3A5%3A%22annee%22%3Bs%3A11%3A%221910+%28vers%29%22%3B%7D&w_fenetre=1260&h_fenetre=994]

